    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a mechanically flawless 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This S54 powerplant features a recently overhauled VANOS unit and verified rod bearings, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with absolute reliability. The chassis has been professionally reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to maintain optimal structural rigidity under load. Power is delivered through the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing and suspension component remains within factory tolerances, preserving the surgical handling and 50/50 weight distribution of this iconic chassis. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
